      automaton\<^sub>3 alphabet\<^sub>3 initial\<^sub>3 transition\<^sub>3 condition\<^sub>3 condition +
    a: automaton_run automaton\<^sub>1 alphabet\<^sub>1 initial\<^sub>1 transition\<^sub>1 condition\<^sub>1 test\<^sub>1 +
